  ;; --- ANNOTATIONS ---
  (text "=== UPPER PCB COMPONENT PLACEMENT ===\n\nJ5: FPC 6-pin 0.5mm connector\n     Center-bottom of board\n     Pin1→3V3, Pin2→GND\n     Pin3→BTN_LEFT, Pin4→BTN_RIGHT\n     Pin5→BTN_BACK, Pin6→BTN_FWD\n\nSW4: Kailh micro switch (Left click)\n     Top-left quadrant, plunger faces UP\n     One pin → BTN_LEFT\n     Other pin → GND\n\nSW5: Kailh micro switch (Right click)\n     Top-right quadrant, plunger faces UP\n     One pin → BTN_RIGHT\n     Other pin → GND\n\nSW6: Side-mount tactile switch (Back)\n     Left edge of board, plunger faces LEFT (outward)\n     One pin → BTN_BACK\n     Other pin → GND\n\nSW7: Side-mount tactile switch (Forward)\n     Right edge of board, plunger faces RIGHT (outward)\n     One pin → BTN_FWD\n     Other pin → GND\n\nC1: 100nF decoupling cap (0402)\n     Near J5, between 3V3 and GND\n\nMounting: 2× M2 holes\n     Aligned with top frame screw posts"
    (at 30 90 0)
